    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i dont know if ppl \"understand\" tho. i feel like i'm just performing a role 24/7 just to keep people from looking at me weird. it feels hopeless like... even if i find \"my people\" i'll still just be tired. it's like a cycle that never ends. why do we even have to keep doing this?",
