    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"letting the performance drop\" doesn't change anything. the world just keeps demanding things from me. it's not like I can just stop existing and have it be okay. it's like there's no way to actually find peace, just different levels of exhaustion. why is it so hard to just... not have to deal with all this?",
